install perl XML modules:

log into client server as root

run "perl -MCPAN -eshell"
  apss0020:${PWD} #perl -MCPAN -eshell
 
  cpan shell -- CPAN exploration and modules installation (v1.59_54)
  ReadLine support available (try 'install Bundle::CPAN')
 
  cpan> 

from cpan> prompt "install Bundle::CPAN"
  ie. install XML::SAX, install XML::Simple

type "quit" to exit from cpan>

from /.cpan/build/new_XML_Module_directory...
perl Makefile.PL - watch for missing requirements, ie XML::Simple needed a parser such as XML::SAX
make test - Watch for how many tests fail, includes around 200 tests
make install - watch for successful completion


